dct_alternative_sm: Map of Wyoming The Undeveloped Empire on the Continental Divide
dct_description_sm: Published by the Clason Map Co. ; Compiled by H. S. Clason. Drawn by L. A. Miller ; Geo. S. Clason ; Issued under the authority of the State Board of Immigration of Wyoming ; Wm. T. Judkins, state immigration agent.
Shows irrigable lands, county lines, drainage, waterways, railroads (including under construction).
Various place names (including camps, ranches, Indian reservations, basins, plateaus).
Back cover has text under "Just a Few Brief facts About the State," inside cover has text under "Come to Wyoming."
